Package org.icesoft.testclient.actor

Interface Summary
Actor The Actor interface defines the methods to be implemented by Classes wishing to act in some meaningful way with a Web Application.
 

Class Summary
ActorBase The ActorBase class just does some commonly necessary things.
BiddingAuctionMonitorActor This actor keeps tracks of the current bid on the first item in the auction monitor.
ChatInteractorActor This Actor sends messages to the simpleChat application.
ChatObserverActor This actor extends the ReceiveUpdatesActor, and allows it to act and parses the returnValue of that Actors act() method.
LoginActor The LoginActor Effectively logs in to the Chat Application.
PingActor  
PingErrorActor This Actor generates a ping request withouth all of the necessary fields.
ReceiveUpdatesActor  
SpoofingActor Use the spoofing actor to fake JSessionID values and ice.session values to secretly pretend to be someone else! Amazing.
SyncTestUpdatesActor This Actor generates a Tab Event between certain textfields.
TimezoneUpdateActor This class generates a string that simulates pressing on various places within the Timezone application.
ViewCreateDestroyActor This actor is constructed with a reference to another actor for the following purpose.
